Datasource.Parameter: (select way, leisure, tourism, landuse, military, power, "natural", amenity, aeroway, building,railway from &prefix;_polygon where (leisure in ('playground', 'nature_reserve', 'park', 'common', 'garden', 'golf_course') or landuse in ('cemetery','forest', 'recreation_ground', 'wood','commercial') or "natural" in ('wood') or amenity in ('graveyard', 'hospital', 'university','college','school','kindergarten') or tourism in ('museum', 'attraction')) and building is null order by z_order,way_area desc) as leisure
(select way, waterway from &prefix;_line where waterway in ('stream','drain','ditch') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') ) as water_lines

(select way,"natural",waterway,landuse,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name from &prefix;_polygon where waterway in ('dock','mill_pond','riverbank','canal') or landuse in ('reservoir','water','basin') or "natural" in ('lake','water','land','bay') order by z_order,way_area desc ) as water_areas
(select way,waterway from &prefix;_line where waterway='river' ) as water_lines

(select way,waterway,disused,lock,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else tunnel end as tunnel from &prefix;_line where waterway in ('weir','river','canal','derelict_canal','stream','drain','ditch','wadi') and (bridge is null or bridge not in ('yes','true','1','aqueduct')) order by z_order ) as water_lines

(select way, case when building in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else building end as building, railway,leisure, amenity, shop, aeroway,tourism from &prefix;_polygon where building is not null or railway='station' or leisure in ('pitch', 'track', 'sports_centre', 'stadium') or amenity in ('public_building', 'townhall','place_of_worship', 'ferry_terminal') or aeroway='terminal' or shop='supermarket' or tourism in ('museum', 'attraction') order by z_order,way_area desc) as building
(select way, highway, tunnel, cycleway, area from &prefix;_line where tunnel in ('yes', 'true', '1') order by z_order) as roads

(select way,highway from &prefix;_polygon where highway in ('residential','unclassified','pedestrian','service','footway','track', 'living_street') and "area" in ('yes', 'true', '1') order by z_order,way_area desc) as roads

(select way, highway, cycleway, area, layer from &prefix;_line where ((tunnel not in ('yes', 'true', '1') or tunnel is null) and (bridge not in ('yes', 'true', '1') or bridge is null)) order by z_order) as roads
(select way, highway, junction from &prefix;_line order by z_order) as roads
(select way, railway, bridge, tunnel from &prefix;_line where "railway" in ('tram', 'light_rail', 'monorail') order by z_order) as roads
(select way, highway, cycleway, area, bridge, layer from &prefix;_line where bridge in ('yes', 'true') order by z_order) as roads
(select way,highway,area from &prefix;_line where oneway in ('yes', 'true', '1') ) as roads
(select way,admin_level from &prefix;_roads where "boundary"='administrative' and admin_level in ('0','1','2','3','4')) as admin
(select way,admin_level from &prefix;_roads where "boundary"='administrative' and admin_level in ('5','6','7','8')) as admin
(select way,admin_level from &prefix;_roads where "boundary"='administrative' and (admin_level is null or admin_level not in ('0','1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8'))) as admin
(select way,place,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name,ref from &prefix;_point where place in ('country','state')) as placenames
(select way,place,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name,ref from &prefix;_point where place in ('city','metropolis','town') and capital='yes') as placenames

(select way,place,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name from &prefix;_point where place in ('city','metropolis','town','large_town','small_town') and (capital is null or capital != 'yes')) as placenames
(select way,place,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name from &prefix;_point where place in ('suburb','village','large_village','hamlet','locality','isolated_dwelling','farm')) as placenames

(select way, COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name, amenity, railway,"natural", man_made, highway, aeroway, shop, tourism, military, access, "historic" from &prefix;_point where amenity IS NOT NULL or railway is NOT NULL or "natural" is NOT NULL or man_made is NOT NULL or highway is NOT NULL or aeroway is NOT NULL or shop is NOT NULL or tourism is NOT NULL or military is NOT NULL or highway is NOT NULL or historic is NOT NULL) as amenity

(select way,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name,amenity,shop,tourism,highway,man_made,access, "natural", military, railway, aeroway, "historic" from &prefix;_polygon where amenity is not null or shop is not null or tourism in ('guest_house','hostel','hotel','museum','viewpoint') or highway in ('bus_stop','traffic_signals')) as points
(select way,highway,area,railway,COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name,ref,oneway,char_length(ref) as length from &prefix;_line) as roads

(select way, way_area, COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name, leisure, landuse, "natural", railway, aeroway, military, amenity, tourism, case when building in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else building end as building, highway, waterway, shop from &prefix;_polygon order by z_order,way_area desc) as leisure

(select way, COALESCE("name:en","int_name",name) as name, "natural", landuse, railway, leisure, aeroway, amenity, shop, tourism, highway, access, man_made, military, building, "historic" from &prefix;_point where (place not in ('city') or place is null)) as points
(select way from &prefix;_line where "addr:interpolation" is not null) as interpolation

(select way,"addr:housenumber" from &prefix;_polygon where "addr:housenumber" is not null and building is not null union select way,"addr:housenumber" from &prefix;_point where "addr:housenumber" is not null ) as housenumbers
